  <Technique
    id={"t23"}
    title={"T23. File-based async mailbox với atomic writes"}
    tid={"F.2"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/swarm/mailbox.py</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> 1–95 · <strong>Layout:</strong> <code>~/.openharness/teams/&lt;team&gt;/agents/&lt;id&gt;/inbox/</code>"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span>
      json, os, uuid, time <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span
      class="kw">import</span> Path <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">Mailbox</span>: <span class="str">"""File-based inbox for a
      single agent. Layout: inbox/ &lt;sort_key&gt;-&lt;uuid&gt;.tmp ← being
      written (atomic) &lt;sort_key&gt;-&lt;uuid&gt;.json ← delivered
      (consumable) """</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">__init__</span>(self, agent_dir: Path): self.inbox = agent_dir
      / <span class="str">"inbox"</span> self.inbox.mkdir(parents=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, exist_ok=<span class="kw">True</span>) <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">send</span>(self, envelope: dict):
      <span class="str">"""Atomic write: write .tmp then rename to
      .json."""</span> sort_key = <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{time.time_ns():020d}"</span> <span class="com"># nanosecond
      for ordering</span> msg_id = uuid.uuid4().hex[:<span class="num">8</span>]
      base = self.inbox / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{sort_key}-{msg_id}"</span> tmp = base.with_suffix(<span
      class="str">".tmp"</span>) final = base.with_suffix(<span
      class="str">".json"</span>) tmp.write_text(json.dumps(envelope,
      ensure_ascii=<span class="kw">False</span>)) os.rename(tmp, final) <span
      class="com"># atomic on POSIX</span> <span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">poll</span>(self, interval=<span
      class="num">0.25</span>): <span class="str">"""Yield envelopes as they
      arrive. Caller deletes after consume."""</span> <span class="kw">while
      True</span>: <span class="kw">for</span> msg_path <span
      class="kw">in</span> sorted(self.inbox.glob(<span
      class="str">"*.json"</span>)): <span class="kw">try</span>: envelope =
      json.loads(msg_path.read_text()) <span class="kw">except</span>
      json.JSONDecodeError: <span class="kw">continue</span> <span class="com">#
      partial write? skip</span> <span class="kw">yield</span> envelope
      msg_path.unlink(missing_ok=<span class="kw">True</span>) <span
      class="kw">await</span> asyncio.sleep(interval) <span class="com">#
      Envelope types (message kinds)</span> <span class="com"># {"kind":
      "user_message", "text": "..."}</span> <span class="com"># {"kind":
      "permission_request", "request_id": "...", "tool": "...", "args":
      {...}}</span> <span class="com"># {"kind": "shutdown", "reason":
      "..."}</span> <span class="com"># {"kind": "tool_result", "tool": "...",
      "result": ..., "is_error": bool}</span></code></pre> <div
      class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong> Mailbox filesystem =
      zero-infra IPC. Atomic write (<code>.tmp</code> → rename) đảm bảo
      <em>reader không bao giờ thấy partial file</em> — rename là atomic trên
      POSIX. Sort-key nano-second đảm bảo thứ tự delivery. Poll loop đơn giản
      (không cần fsnotify) — latency 250ms acceptable. Envelope kind enum →
      message-kind routing trong consumer. Không cần Redis/RabbitMQ/Kafka →
      scale đến ~10 agent thoải mái.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4>
      <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> os, json, uuid, time, asyncio
      <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span class="kw">import</span> Path
      <span class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">FileMailbox</span>: <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">__init__</span>(self, inbox: Path):
      self.inbox = inbox; inbox.mkdir(parents=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      exist_ok=<span class="kw">True</span>) <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">send</span>(self, msg: dict): sort_key = <span
      class="fn">f</span><span class="str">"{time.time_ns():020d}"</span> mid =
      uuid.uuid4().hex[:<span class="num">8</span>] tmp = self.inbox / <span
      class="fn">f</span><span class="str">"{sort_key}-{mid}.tmp"</span> final =
      self.inbox / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{sort_key}-{mid}.json"</span> tmp.write_text(json.dumps(msg))
      os.rename(tmp, final) <span class="com"># atomic</span> <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">receive</span>(self): <span
      class="kw">while True</span>: <span class="kw">for</span> p <span
      class="kw">in</span> sorted(self.inbox.glob(<span
      class="str">"*.json"</span>)): msg = json.loads(p.read_text()) p.unlink()
      <span class="kw">yield</span> msg <span class="kw">await</span>
      asyncio.sleep(<span class="num">0.25</span>)</code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Zero-infra (không cần message broker)",
        "Atomic rename — no partial reads",
        "FIFO order qua nanosecond sort key",
        "Inspectable bằng filesystem tools (ls, cat)",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Poll interval 250ms → latency floor",
        "Filesystem bottleneck khi nhiều agent",
        "Không persistence across machine (no remote)",
        "Cần cleanup stale message nếu reader crash",
      ]}
    />
    <RefList
      items={[
        '<a href="https://lwn.net/Articles/820462/">LWN — File-based IPC patterns</a>',
        '<a href="https://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/patterns/messaging/">Enterprise Integration Patterns — Messaging Mailbox</a>',
        '<a href="https://redis.io/glossary/message-queue/">Redis — Message queue patterns (comparison)</a>',
      ]}
    />
  </Technique>
  <Technique
    id={"t24"}
    title={"T24. Dual-channel permission sync protocol"}
    tid={"F.3"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/swarm/permission_sync.py</code> · <strong>Channels:</strong> file (<code>pending/</code> + <code>resolved/</code>) + mailbox"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span>
      json, time <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span
      class="kw">import</span> Path <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">PermissionSync</span>: <span class="str">"""Worker writes
      pending request; Leader resolves by writing resolution."""</span> <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">__init__</span>(self, team_dir:
      Path, agent_id: str): self.pending_dir = team_dir / <span
      class="str">"permissions"</span> / <span class="str">"pending"</span>
      self.resolved_dir = team_dir / <span class="str">"permissions"</span> /
      <span class="str">"resolved"</span> self.pending_dir.mkdir(parents=<span
      class="kw">True</span>, exist_ok=<span class="kw">True</span>)
      self.resolved_dir.mkdir(parents=<span class="kw">True</span>,
      exist_ok=<span class="kw">True</span>) self.agent_id = agent_id <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">worker_request</span>(self,
      tool: str, tool_input: dict, *, timeout=<span class="num">300</span>):
      <span class="str">"""Called by worker: write pending request; wait for
      resolution file."""</span> request_id = uuid.uuid4().hex <span
      class="com"># Fast-path: read-only tools auto-approved without leader
      involvement</span> <span class="kw">if</span>
      _is_read_only_heuristic(tool, tool_input): <span class="kw">return</span>
      PermissionResolution(approved=<span class="kw">True</span>, reason=<span
      class="str">"read-only"</span>) pending_file = self.pending_dir / <span
      class="fn">f</span><span class="str">"{request_id}.json"</span>
      resolved_file = self.resolved_dir / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{request_id}.json"</span>
      pending_file.write_text(json.dumps({ <span
      class="str">"request_id"</span>: request_id, <span
      class="str">"agent_id"</span>: self.agent_id, <span
      class="str">"tool"</span>: tool, <span class="str">"tool_input"</span>:
      tool_input, <span class="str">"ts"</span>: time.time(), })) <span
      class="com"># Also send notification via mailbox for low-latency
      wake-up</span> <span class="kw">await</span>
      self._notify_leader_via_mailbox(request_id) <span class="com"># Poll for
      resolution</span> deadline = time.time() + timeout <span
      class="kw">while</span> time.time() &lt; deadline: <span
      class="kw">if</span> resolved_file.exists(): data =
      json.loads(resolved_file.read_text()) pending_file.unlink(missing_ok=<span
      class="kw">True</span>) resolved_file.unlink(missing_ok=<span
      class="kw">True</span>) <span class="kw">return</span>
      PermissionResolution(**data) <span class="kw">await</span>
      asyncio.sleep(<span class="num">0.25</span>) <span
      class="kw">return</span> PermissionResolution(approved=<span
      class="kw">False</span>, reason=<span class="str">"timeout"</span>) <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">leader_resolve</span>(self,
      request_id: str, approved: bool, *, reason=<span class="str">""</span>):
      <span class="str">"""Called by leader (main UI) when user
      approves/denies."""</span> resolved_file = self.resolved_dir / <span
      class="fn">f</span><span class="str">"{request_id}.json"</span> tmp =
      resolved_file.with_suffix(<span class="str">".tmp"</span>)
      tmp.write_text(json.dumps({<span class="str">"approved"</span>: approved,
      <span class="str">"reason"</span>: reason})) os.rename(tmp,
      resolved_file)</code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan
      trọng:</strong> Worker (subprocess) cần approval từ leader (main CLI)
      nhưng không share memory. Dual-channel: (1) <strong>file</strong> —
      persistent, auditable, survive crash; (2) <strong>mailbox</strong> —
      low-latency wake-up signal (không cần poll sát). Read-only heuristic
      auto-approve → giảm tải leader. Pattern đồng bộ: worker <em>blocks</em>
      trên poll, leader <em>non-blocking</em> write resolution → clean
      separation.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4> <pre><code><span
      class="kw">import</span> os, json, time, asyncio, uuid <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">PermSync</span>: <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">__init__</span>(self, pending_dir,
      resolved_dir): self.p = pending_dir; self.r = resolved_dir <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">worker_wait</span>(self,
      tool, args, timeout=<span class="num">300</span>): rid = uuid.uuid4().hex
      (self.p / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{rid}.json"</span>).write_text(json.dumps({<span
      class="str">"tool"</span>: tool, <span class="str">"args"</span>: args}))
      resolved = self.r / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{rid}.json"</span> deadline = time.time() + timeout <span
      class="kw">while</span> time.time() &lt; deadline: <span
      class="kw">if</span> resolved.exists(): data =
      json.loads(resolved.read_text()) resolved.unlink() <span
      class="kw">return</span> data[<span class="str">"approved"</span>] <span
      class="kw">await</span> asyncio.sleep(<span class="num">0.25</span>) <span
      class="kw">return False</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">leader_resolve</span>(self, rid, approved): tmp = self.r /
      <span class="fn">f</span><span class="str">"{rid}.tmp"</span>
      tmp.write_text(json.dumps({<span class="str">"approved"</span>:
      approved})) os.rename(tmp, self.r / <span class="fn">f</span><span
      class="str">"{rid}.json"</span>)</code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Persistent + auditable — crash-resilient",
        "Dual channel (file persist + mailbox latency)",
        "Read-only heuristic giảm leader load",
        "Atomic rename ở leader side",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Poll loop 250ms floor — không real-time",
        "Stale pending file nếu worker crash",
        'Heuristic "read-only" có thể miss case',
        "Không có request priority / queue",
      ]}
    />
