  <Technique
    id={"t26"}
    title={"T26. YAML agent definitions + coordinator dispatch"}
    tid={"F.5"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/coordinator/agent_definitions.py</code> · <strong>Load:</strong> <code>.openharness/agents/*.yaml</code>"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span>
      yaml <span class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span class="kw">import</span>
      Path <span class="kw">from</span> pydantic <span class="kw">import</span>
      BaseModel <span class="kw">from</span> openharness.permissions.modes <span
      class="kw">import</span> PermissionMode <span class="kw">class</span>
      <span class="type">AgentDefinition</span>(BaseModel): name: str
      description: str system_prompt: str tools: list[str] = [] <span
      class="com"># allowlist (empty = all)</span> disallowed_tools: list[str] =
      [] <span class="com"># denylist</span> model: str = <span
      class="str">"claude-sonnet-4-6"</span> effort: str = <span
      class="str">"medium"</span> <span class="com"># low/medium/high</span>
      permission_mode: PermissionMode = PermissionMode.DEFAULT max_turns: int |
      <span class="kw">None</span> = <span class="num">50</span> color: str =
      <span class="str">"cyan"</span> isolation: str = <span
      class="str">"none"</span> <span class="com"># "none" | "worktree"</span>
      <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">load_agent_definitions</span>(cwd: Path) -&gt; dict[str,
      AgentDefinition]: defs = {} <span class="kw">for</span> location <span
      class="kw">in</span> [ cwd / <span class="str">".openharness"</span> /
      <span class="str">"agents"</span>, Path.home() / <span
      class="str">".openharness"</span> / <span class="str">"agents"</span>, ]:
      <span class="kw">if not</span> location.is_dir(): <span
      class="kw">continue</span> <span class="kw">for</span> f <span
      class="kw">in</span> sorted(location.glob(<span
      class="str">"*.yaml"</span>)): data = yaml.safe_load(f.read_text()) <span
      class="kw">for</span> entry <span class="kw">in</span> (data <span
      class="kw">if</span> isinstance(data, list) <span class="kw">else</span>
      [data]): defn = AgentDefinition(**entry) defs[defn.name] = defn <span
      class="kw">return</span> defs <span class="com"># Example agent definition
      YAML:</span> <span class="com"># name: doc-writer</span> <span
      class="com"># description: Writes technical documentation</span> <span
      class="com"># system_prompt: |</span> <span class="com"># You are a doc
      writer. Focus on clarity, accuracy, and structure.</span> <span
      class="com"># tools: [Read, Write, Grep, Glob]</span> <span class="com">#
      permission_mode: plan # cannot mutate</span> <span class="com">#
      max_turns: 30</span> <span class="com"># isolation: worktree # get own
      worktree</span> <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">Coordinator</span>: <span class="str">"""Central router:
      decide which agent handles an incoming task."""</span> <span
      class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">__init__</span>(self, definitions:
      dict[str, AgentDefinition]): self.definitions = definitions self.manager =
      BackgroundTaskManager() <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">dispatch</span>(self, task_description: str, preferred_agent:
      str | <span class="kw">None</span> = <span class="kw">None</span>): defn =
      self.definitions.get(preferred_agent) <span class="kw">or</span>
      self._pick_agent(task_description) worktree = <span
      class="kw">await</span> create_worktree(...) <span class="kw">if</span>
      defn.isolation == <span class="str">"worktree"</span> <span
      class="kw">else None</span> <span class="kw">return await</span>
      self.manager.create_agent_task(defn, worktree=worktree)</code></pre> <div
      class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong> Declarative agent
      definition → dễ version control, review, share. Coordinator là central
      dispatcher: đọc task description, chọn agent phù hợp (hoặc
      <code>preferred_agent</code> name hint), spawn với config tương ứng.
      <code>isolation: worktree</code> kích hoạt T25 (git worktree). Permission
      mode per-agent nghĩa một agent có thể <code>plan</code> (research only)
      trong khi agent khác <code>full_auto</code> (background CI worker). Rất
      giống pattern Claude Code subagents.</div> <h4>Code example (generic)</h4>
      <pre><code><span class="kw">import</span> yaml <span
      class="kw">from</span> pathlib <span class="kw">import</span> Path <span
      class="kw">from</span> pydantic <span class="kw">import</span> BaseModel
      <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">AgentDef</span>(BaseModel): name: str; description: str;
      system_prompt: str tools: list[str] = [] model: str = <span
      class="str">"claude-sonnet-4-6"</span> max_turns: int = <span
      class="num">50</span> isolation: str = <span class="str">"none"</span>
      <span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">load_defs</span>(dir: Path)
      -&gt; <span class="kw">dict</span>[str, AgentDef]: out = {} <span
      class="kw">for</span> f <span class="kw">in</span> sorted(dir.glob(<span
      class="str">"*.yaml"</span>)): d = yaml.safe_load(f.read_text()) <span
      class="kw">for</span> entry <span class="kw">in</span> (d <span
      class="kw">if</span> isinstance(d, list) <span class="kw">else</span>
      [d]): defn = AgentDef(**entry) out[defn.name] = defn <span
      class="kw">return</span> out <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">Coordinator</span>: <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">dispatch</span>(self, task: str, agent_name: str): defn =
      self.defs[agent_name] wt = <span class="kw">await</span>
      make_worktree(repo, agent_name) <span class="kw">if</span> defn.isolation
      == <span class="str">"worktree"</span> <span class="kw">else None</span>
      <span class="kw">return await</span> self.spawn(defn, wt,
      task)</code></pre>
